<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Application Accepted</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { width: 80%; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
    .header { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .footer { font-size: 0.8em; text-align: center; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #007bff; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Your application for the campaign <strong>"<%= campaignTitle %>"</strong> has been <strong>ACCEPTED</strong>!</p>
      <p>The brand is excited to work with you. Please log in to your dashboard to see the next steps and collaboration details.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Kollab. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
